{"type":"message","id":"05e88ebb","parentId":"21de01af","timestamp":"2026-03-10T01:07:09.384Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_Ri3hRzd2jybODjDZu7WhUJsR","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Improvement Proposals\n\n## Overview\nGenerated by OC-System-Evolver Improvement Engine at 2026-03-09T18:00:14.088120\n\n## Proposal Status Key\n- **DRAFT**: Initial proposal, not yet analyzed\n- **ANALYZED**: Technical analysis complete\n- **CLASSIFIED**: Risk classification assigned\n- **PLANNED**: Change plan created\n- **APPROVED**: Ready for execution\n- **EXECUTING**: Currently being implemented\n- **COMPLETED**: Successfully implemented\n- **FAILED**: Implementation failed\n- **ROLLED_BACK**: Change reverted\n\n## Active Proposals\n\n### IMP-001: Degraded Skill\n- **Status**: COMPLETED\n- **Created**: 2026-03-09T18:00:14.087722\n- **Resolved**: 2026-03-06T18:31:00.000000 (previously repaired)\n- **Type**: Risk Mitigation\n- **Priority**: MEDIUM\n- **Estimated Effort**: 30 minutes\n- **Actual Effort**: Already completed\n\n#### Problem Detected\nDegraded Skill\n\n#### Evidence\nSkill vector-memory is missing SKILL.md or scripts directory\n- **Recommendation**: Check skill structure at /home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/skills/vector-memory\n\n#### Investigation Results\nThe vector-memory skill was already repaired on 2026-03-06:\n- ✅ SKILL.md file exists and is valid (4900 bytes)\n- ✅ scripts directory exists with 13 script files\n- ✅ REPAIR_DOCUMENTATION.md confirms repair completion\n- ✅ Current health report shows skill as HEALTHY (95/100 skills health)\n\n#### Root Cause\nOutdated health report (2026-03-06) was being referenced. Fresh health check shows:\n- **Old health score**: 84/100 (vector-memory: DEGRADED)\n- **New health score**: 90/100 (vector-memory: HEALTHY)\n- **Skills health improved**: 75/100 → 95/100\n\n#### Verification\n- ✅ Ran fresh system observation\n- ✅ Confirmed vector-memory skill structure\n- ✅ Updated health r